articles.title: Pre-Monty Python series 'The Complete and Utter History of Britain' unearthed, streaming in full for first time - Brooklyn Vegan
articles.description: 'The Complete and Utter History of Britain' was created by Michael Palin and Terry Jones and aired in 1969 right before Monty Python formed. Most of the episodes were thought lost.
